@model string

@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Cuenta Activada";
    Layout = "_LayoutSimple";
}

<div class="w-100 text-center py-5 d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
    
    <!-- Editorial Element -->
    <div class="mb-5 d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
        <div class="position-relative">
            <div class="rounded-circle bg-secondary-container d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center position-relative z-10" style="width: 6rem; height: 6rem;">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-secondary-container fs-1 icon-fill-1" data-icon="verified_user">verified_user</span>
            </div>
            <!-- Decorative blur element -->
            <div class="position-absolute rounded-circle border border-white-10" style="width: 3rem; height: 3rem; top: -1rem; right: -1rem; background-color: rgba(233, 193, 118, 0.2); backdrop-filter: blur(4px);"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="font-headline fw-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tighter mb-4" style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);">
        Cuenta Activada
    </h1>
    
    <p class="text-secondary-custom lh-lg mb-5 mx-auto px-3" style="font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 2vw, 1.25rem); max-width: 36rem;">
        Bienvenido/a <strong>@Model</strong>, sus credenciales institucionales han sido validadas correctamente. Ya tiene acceso completo a la consola de gestión de perfiles.
    </p>
    
    <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row align-items-center justify-content-center gap-3 gap-md-4 mb-5 pb-5">
        <a href="@Url.Action("Login", "Account")" class="btn premium-gradient text-white font-headline fw-semibold px-5 py-3 rounded-3 shadow hover-scale-101 active-scale-95 transition-all d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center gap-2">
            Ir al inicio de sesión
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined fs-6" data-icon="arrow_forward">arrow_forward</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-secondary border-outline-variant text-secondary-custom font-headline fw-semibold px-5 py-3 rounded-3 hover-bg-surface-container-low transition-all border-opacity-25 bg-white">
            Contactar Soporte
        </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Info Cards Grid -->
    <div class="row w-100 g-4 pb-5" style="max-width: 72rem; text-align: left;">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
            <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-4 p-md-5 rounded-4 shadow-sm hover-shadow transition-all h-100 border border-light">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-tertiary-container" style="color: #b6924c;" data-icon="security">security</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-headline fw-bold text-primary-custom fs-5 mb-2">Acceso Seguro</h3>
                <p class="text-on-surface-variant small lh-lg m-0">Su acceso incorpora múltiples filtros de seguridad y trazabilidad transaccional en tiempo real.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
            <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-4 p-md-5 rounded-4 shadow-sm hover-shadow transition-all h-100 border border-light">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-tertiary-container" style="color: #b6924c;" data-icon="account_circle">account_circle</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-headline fw-bold text-primary-custom fs-5 mb-2">Gobernanza de Identidad</h3>
                <p class="text-on-surface-variant small lh-lg m-0">Gestión centralizada de perfiles y credenciales institucionales sincronizadas automáticamente.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
            <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-4 p-md-5 rounded-4 shadow-sm hover-shadow transition-all h-100 border border-light">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-tertiary-container" style="color: #b6924c;" data-icon="support_agent">support_agent</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-headline fw-bold text-primary-custom fs-5 mb-2">Soporte Prioritario</h3>
                <p class="text-on-surface-variant small lh-lg m-0">El estado de su cuenta le otorga acceso directo a nuestra línea preferencial de asistencia técnica.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
